  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <div type="mūlam" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV18">
      <l>kātaṉ mikaviṉ vāyviṭu kiḷaviyun</l>
<l>tōḻi ciṟaippuṟat tēkiṭu kiḷaviyuñ</l>
<l>ceṟippaṟi vuṟuttaluñ cūḷeṉa niṉaittalu</l>
<l>miṟappa nuvaṟalu miruḷvara vēṇṭalu</l>
<l>maṟuttalu nērtaluṅ kuṟiyiṭam vakuttalum</l>
<l>nayappa moḻitalu mavaṉvara vuṇarttaluṅ</l>
<l>kuṟittuḻi yuyttalum peyarcciyo ṭalkuṟic</l>
<l>ciṟaippuṟa mākac ceppalu nōtalu</l>
<l>miṟaippuṟa mākiya viravuk kuṟiyē.</l></lg>
</div>
</body>
</text>
<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <head xml:lang="en">Commentary</head>
      <p xml:id="TNV18comm1">eṉpatu iravuk kuṟi yām āṟuṇarttutaṉutaliṟṟu.</p>
      <p xml:lang="en">The quoted [<hi rend="italic">cūttiram</hi>] intend to make known the way in which 
      the nighttime tryst occurs.</p>
      <p xml:id="TNV18comm2">vāy viṭu kiḷavi mutal ākat talaimakaṉeñcoṭu nōtal īṟākac collap paṭṭaṉa vil 
      varai ikavā viravuk kuṟi yām eṉṟa vāṟu.</p>
      <p xml:lang="en">The things mentioned, beginning with 'speech [where she] divulges' and ending with 'the hero aching with his heart', are the nighttime tryst that occurs outside the boundary of the house.</p>
 <div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem1"> 
        <l>aṭumpiṉ meṉkoṭi tumiyak kaṭumpakaṟ</l>
        <l>koṭuṅkaḻi maruṅkiṉvan takaṉṟa</l>
        <l>neṭuntē raṇṇalpiṉ ceṉṟate ṉeñcē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu1">eṉpatu talaimakaḷ āṟṟāmaik kaṇ vāy viṭu kiḷavi.</p>
    </div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem2"> 
        <l>cevvā yaṉṉaniṉ cēvalu nīyum</l>
        <l>kaivē laṇṇalaik kaḻaṟi</l>
        <l>ṉeytuva tuḷatō viyampumi ṉemakkē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu2">eṉpatu ituvum atu.</p>
    </div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem3"> 
        <l>āykatirc celva ṉattañ cērnteṉa</l>
        <l>nōykūr neñciṉa ḷuḻappap</l>
        <l>pōyiṉa mātō puḷḷiṉam pirintē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu3">eṉpatu talaimakaṉ ciṟaip puṟam ākap piṟitiṉ mēl vaittut tōḻi kūṟiyatu.</p>
    </div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem4"> 
        <l>mālai maṇantu kālaip piriyuṅ</l>
        <l>kātala ruṭaiyaiyō kaṟainīṅku matiya</l>
        <l>miravē yāyi ṉallai pakalē</l>
        <l>melliyaṟ koṭicci nutaliṉum</l>
        <l>pulleṉ ṟaṉaiyā ṉōkō yāṉē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu4">eṉpatu ituvum atu.</p>
    </div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem5"> 
        <l>aṉṉai vāḻi nerunaṉ mātar</l>
        <l>meṉmulai yarumpiya vākamu</l>
        <l>meṉṉum paṉmuṟai nōkkiṉa ḷiṉitē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu5">eṉpatu kuṟippiṉāṟ ceṟippaṟivuṟuttatu.</p> 
    </div>
 <div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem6"> 
        <l>pāṅkiṉa rākit tīṅkutalait tarunari</l>
        <l>ṉīṅkup pirivu cūḻntaṉṟa</l>
        <l>yāṅkaṉa moḻikō vēṅkaiyatu viṉaiyē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu6">eṉpatu ciṟaip puṟattuc ceṟippaṟi vuṟuttatu.</p>
    </div>
 <div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem7"> 
        <l>uraiyā yaṇṇal ceytiṟa muritaṉiṉ</l>
        <l>viraivāy vēṅkai viriyak</l>
        <l>kuralcāyn toḻintateṅ koypuṉat tiṉaiyē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu7">eṉpatu veḷip paṭac ceṟippaṟivuṟuttatu.</p> 
    </div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem8"> 
        <l>ammeṉ cāya lāyiḻai tiṟattup</l>
        <l>poymmai niṉvā yuḷateṉiṉ</l>
        <l>meymmai yārō viḷampiṉar piṟarē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu8">eṉpatu cūḷ eṉa niṉaintatu.</p>
    </div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem9" corresp="#KT18">
        <l>vēral vēli vērkkōṭ palaviṉ</l>
        <l>cāra ṉāṭa cevviyai yākumati</l>
        <l>yāraḵ taṟintici ṉōrē cāraṟ</l>
        <l>ciṟukōṭṭup perumpaḻan tūṅki yāṅkiva</l>
        <l>ḷuyirtavac ciṟitu kāmamō peritē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu9">eṉpatu āṟṟāḷ eṉpatu paṭak kūṟiyatu.</p>
</div> 
 <div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem10">
        <l>oḷḷiṇar vēṅkai yoḷḷiṇar vēṅkainiṉ</l>
        <l>kiḷaiyoṭu makiḻāk kiḷaitapu vēṅkai</l>
        <l>nīyē malartan tōyē</l>
        <l>yāyō veṉuṅkura lāvayiṟ kaṭintē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu10">eṉpatu eṉa varuvaṉavuṅ koḷka.</p>
</div>                      
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem11">
        <l>varivaḷait tōḷi yorutaṉi yoḻiyap</l>
        <l>piritu meṉṟi yāyiṟ peritaḻintu</l>
        <l>pariyal vāḻiyō neñcē</l>
        <l>iruḷiṭai yeytalu meytumā<!--note place="foot">A <hi rend="italic">figura etymologica</hi> as found in TNV17poem15: <p xml:lang="ta">alavaṉ āṭṭalum āṭṭāḷ...</p></note--> ṉamakkē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu11">eṉpatu iruḷ varal vēṇṭal.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem12">
        <l>niraitā raṇṇa ṉeṭuṅkaḻai yukutta</l>
        <l>virikatir nittilam parattali</l>
        <l>ṉiravum pakalpōṉ ṟilaṅkumā livaṇē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu12">eṉpatu iraviṉ varutal ariteṉṟatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem13">
        <l>tērā ṉallaṉ pēruṇar viṉṉē</l>
        <l>yikantō ṉalla ṉaṉpuperi tuṭaiya</l>
        <l>ṉiṉaiyō ṉiṉaiya ṉākutaṉ</l>
        <l>maṉaṉiṟai kuṉṟa vāṟṟā māṟē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu13">eṉpatu nērtal.</p>
    </div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem14">
        <l>naṟaikamaḻ cāntameñ cāntē pūvum</l>
        <l>poṟaimali kāntaḷam pūvē yāṭiṭañ</l>
        <l>ciṟaivaṇ ṭārkkuñ ceyalaiyam poḻilē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu14">eṉpatu iravuk kuṟi yiṭaṅ kūṟiṟṟu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem15">
        <l>vēypayi liṟumpiṉ viyalaṟaic cilampiṉ</l>
        <l>vālveḷ ḷaruvi muḻaviṟ ṟatumpuñ</l>
        <l>cēyuyar māmalaic cilampaṉu</l>
        <l>māynuta larivai yarukiṉaṉ peritē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu15">eṉpatu iravuk kuṟi nayappittatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem16" corresp="#KT88">
        <l>oliveḷ ḷaruvi yōṅkumalai nāṭaṉ</l>
        <l>ciṟukaṭ peruṅkaḷiṟu vayappuli tākkit</l>
        <l>toṉmuraṇ cōrun tuṉṉaruñ cōlai</l>
        <l>naṭunāḷ varutalum varūum</l>
        <l>vaṭunā ṇalamē tōḻi nāmē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu16">eṉpatu maṟuttatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem17">
        <l>koṭuvari vayappuli tākkak kolaiyuyntu</l>
        <l>naṭunāḷ yāmat taruñcura nīntip</l>
        <l>pativayiṟ pukuntōṟ kiyāvatuṅ</l>
        <l>katavan tiṟattal kaṉaṅkuḻai kaṭaṉē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu17">eṉpatu valitākac colli nayappittatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem18">
        <l>puḷḷun tuyilpuṭai peyarntaṉa puṉaluḷ</l>
        <l>vaḷḷitaḻp puṉṉai maṇikkāy vīḻum</l>
        <l>vantaṉaṉ kollō tāṉē</l>
        <l>ventiṟa laṇṇa ṉiṉaintaṉaṉ viraintē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu18">eṉpatu tōḻi varavuṇarntatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem19">
        <l>aṉṉā yaṉṉāy kāṇeṉ ṟirumuṟai</l>
        <l>taṉyā ṉeṭuppavun tuyiṉmaṭin taṉaḷē</l>
        <l>yilaṅkilai neṭuvē leṭuttalum</l>
        <l>pulamputuya rakalak kuṟivan tōṉē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu19">eṉpatu varavuṇarttiyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem20">
        <l>kaḷḷaviḻ kōtaitaṉ kaṇpōṟ kuvaḷaiyum</l>
        <l>muḷḷeyi ṟarumpu mullaiyum</l>
        <l>koḷkuvam pōtunaṅ kuḷirpoḻi liṭattē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu20">eṉpatu talaimakaṉ varavuṇarntu tōḻi talaimakaḷaik kuṟi vayiṉ uyttatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV18poem21">
        <l>kāvi kaṇṭaṉai yāyiṟ ṟūvi</l>
        <l>mayilēr cāyaṟ kuyilēr kiḷavi</l>
        <l>peyarntaṉai yaruḷal vēṇṭu</l>
        <l>miṅkivai kāṇiya veṉṉoṭum puṇarntē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV18koḷu21">eṉpatu koṇṭu nīṅkal.</p>
</div>
